    "W":  {"lz_peak_w_m3": 2.584e-31, "te_peak_eV": 1640.9, "used_in_cooling_curve": false, "note": "cross-check only; the cooling curve keeps the cited Putterich 2010 value (~1e-31). Tungsten Lz spans ~1e-31 (Putterich) to ~4.7e-31 (Mavrin 2018) across atomic-data sources; the ~1640 eV peak location is consistent."}
