  "notes": "Peak magnitudes for C/Ne/Ar are dominated by line radiation (PLT), so they are robust to the recombination/continuum (PRB) charge-state indexing. The ADAS96 C/Ne values (~5.8e-32) are below the older Post & Jensen 1977 estimate (~2e-31)."
